<Entry TID="7" language="en" translation="This is a template geodata model to be used for modeling according CHBase, the &quot;base modules of the Swiss Confederation for minimal geodata models&quot;.&#10;&#10;Prepare your model according CHBase by importing the needed CHBase packages (i.e. modules) to your model.&#10;&#10;Start modeling! Make sure to apply CHBase definitions wherever appropriate!&#10;&#10;Questions? drop a line at &quot;models@geo.admin.ch&quot;"/>
</ch.ehi.basics.types.NlsString>
